Message.SourceString: Ah, hello, this thing on? Apprentice, well done, you've got yourself an orb. This is the first step toward creating your very own magical staff.

Message.SourceString: Alright, it's recording. Hello apprentice, well done on charging up that orb.

Message.SourceString: This orb is the heart of a very special staff known as the Staff of Light. Popular with blue robed wizards throughout Saradomin's domain.

Message.SourceString: Now we just attach the orb to the shaft and voila, one staff of light. Great job, apprentice!

Message.SourceString: Now Jules, turn this thing off so I can hit you with this broom without it being preserved for future generations.
